21:33.158 --> 21:35.727
I'm going to place one
of the kings on top.

21:35.761 --> 21:36.795
Here.

21:36.828 --> 21:38.997
And one of the kings on bottom.

21:39.031 --> 21:41.500
And I'm going to lose this card

21:41.533 --> 21:43.235
here in the middle.

21:43.268 --> 21:45.270
Here.

21:45.304 --> 21:47.005
And I clearly show
that it's still there,

21:47.039 --> 21:48.907
that it has not
been teleported...

21:48.940 --> 21:50.275
yet.

21:50.309 --> 21:51.276
Okay?

21:51.310 --> 21:52.511
Your card lost,

21:52.544 --> 21:53.979
and at the count of three,

21:54.012 --> 21:56.515
the two kings
and your chosen card.

21:56.548 --> 21:59.718
One, two, and three.

21:59.751 --> 22:02.020
