29:07.712 --> 29:09.547
Okay.
I'm sure you recognize this.

29:09.581 --> 29:10.648
- Uh-huh.

29:10.682 --> 29:13.151
- You think
it's a children's toy,

29:13.184 --> 29:15.653
a puzzle to be solved,

29:15.687 --> 29:18.323
