29:19.224 --> 29:22.127
But it also has
magical properties

29:22.160 --> 29:23.962
for the right puzzle.

29:23.995 --> 29:26.931
Please mix up.

29:26.965 --> 29:29.033
- Any way?
- Yeah.

29:29.067 --> 29:31.035
Very mixed.
- Okay.

29:31.069 --> 29:33.938
So just a few turns
is all we need.

29:33.972 --> 29:36.608
- Well...
- And do you know, Alyson?

29:36.641 --> 29:38.143
The cube...
- Yeah.

29:38.176 --> 29:40.845
- Can magically--
magically absorbs color

29:40.879 --> 29:43.748
