29:46.584 --> 29:47.652
- Okay.

29:47.685 --> 29:51.122
- All we need
is a single color

29:51.156 --> 29:53.591
like this bag.

29:53.625 --> 29:54.926
- Mm.

29:54.959 --> 29:56.795
